Summer Fair 2026 Activities Licensing
==========================

Scope
-----

Unless a file says otherwise, this repository uses a split licensing model:

1. Source code and project-authored technical assets are licensed under the MIT License.
2. Project-authored non-code content is licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0).
3. Third-party vendored dependencies keep their own original licenses and are not re-licensed by this file.

Original project-authored material in this repository is created by Joe Hudson,
made using agentic development methods, unless a file states otherwise.

What Counts As Code Under MIT
-----------------------------

The MIT License applies to project-authored source files such as:

- HTML, CSS, and JavaScript in this repository
- project-authored inline SVG/data-URI artwork embedded in source files
- project-authored configuration and workflow files

