Notes On Images And Celebration Icons
-------------------------------------

- public/images currently contains no standalone image assets.
- The success-state flower, parrot, palm, and shell visuals are Unicode emoji characters
  in public/bubble-sort.html, rendered by the user's platform emoji font at runtime.
- The repository does not currently bundle separate image files for those celebration icons.
